    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains pristine with the original factory scent and zero signs of wear on the upholstery. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotless, reflecting meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
